originalText.text: Dr. Philips is extremely patient and kind. I was struggling during my first trimester and she listened deeply to what I was saying and provided me with a lot of knowledge and hope. She even ran some extra blood tests to rule out some things I was nervous about. She a very good and incredibly caring doctor. I highly recommend her!
